com.github.dandelion.core.storage

Interface AssetStorage

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractAssetStorage, MemoryAssetStorage

    public interface AssetStorage

    Interface for an asset storage.

    Custom implementations should extends AbstractAssetStorage instead of implementing this interface.

    Since:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Thibault Duchateau
